data.eml:eml: Larvae of Amphipsyche species (Trichoptera: Hydropsychidae) from Thailand

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Peumwarunyoo, Pronthip, Prommi, Taeng-On (2013): Larvae of Amphipsyche species (Trichoptera: Hydropsychidae) from Thailand. Zootaxa 3635 (3): 251-260, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3635.3.4
